NianWeapon: {
	1: {
		Desc: DEF +70%, ATK +45%, and normal attacks now deal Arts damage \n[c/00FF00:During the skill, Nian smashes the large shield in her hands toward enemies, dealing 100% magic damage.]
		Label: Tin Burning
	}

	2: {
		Label: Copper Seal
		Desc: Stops attacking; DEF +130%, Block +1, upon receiving an enemy attack, deals Arts damage to the attacker equal to 90% of Nian's ATK and silences them for 5 seconds. \n[c/00FF00:The original block-based counter damage and silence effects are disabled. Instead, every 0.5 seconds, enemies within a certain range take 50% source-less magic damage.]
	}

	3: {
		Desc: ATK +120%; Nearby allied Operators gain DEF +80%, Block +1 and status resistance.\n[c/00FF00:The original resistance and ally defense/block bonuses are disabled. The large shield now follows the mouse to attack, dealing 100% physical damage.]
		Label: Iron Defense
	}
}

